            "title": "創想三維收升僅21%  一手帳面賺600元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今天首掛創想三維(03388)收升21.27%，報22.8元，一手150股帳面賺600元。成交10.14億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"創想三維科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/Creality-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"創想三維科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/Creality-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">創想三維科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一度高見34元，較招股價18.8元升15.2元升80.85%，一手帳面賺2280元。</p>\n</div>",
