            "title": "全日收市｜港股升176點成交破4600億   手機股午後強勢   恒指5月累跌逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股全日升176點，成交高達4620億元以上，一周計恒指跌1.65%，5 月累逾2% ; 恒生科技指數一周及5 月俱微升，恒生國企指數跑輸。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">聯想(00992)、舜宇(02382)、信達生物(01801)俱報雙位數升幅，電動車股插水，晶片股隨A股回落。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_01801-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_01801-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-121226__source-web_理想汽車-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-121226__source-web_理想汽車-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：理想汽車官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_01801-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-121226__source-web_理想汽車-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：理想汽車官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數全日升176點或0.7%，報25182，今早開升155點或0.62%，報25161點，高開後偏軟，一度見25055，升49點或0.19%，為全日低位，即大幅向上，最高見25313，升307點或1.22%，午後區間波動。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數午後倒跌，全日跌4點或0.09%，報4884點，今早開升51點或1.05%，報4939點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生國企指數全日升61點或0.73%，報8425點，今早開升41點或0.5%，報8406點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交4620.7億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一周計恒指跌424點或1.65%，5月跌576點或2.23% ; 科指升15點或0.3%，5月累升13點或0.26% ; 國指一周跌125點或1.46%，5 月累跌256點或2.94%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6月期指升303點或1.22%，報25148，低水133點 ; 科指期貨半日報4960點，升87點或1.79%，低水10點 ; 國指期貨半日升120點或1.45%，報8421點，低水50點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>聯想控股飆逾12%</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">聯想(00992)全日飛升21.95%，報24元，成交居第三位，為表現最佳藍籌股，推升恒指46點，成升市功臣，最高25.7元，升30.58%，為歷史新高，戴爾季績及指引遠勝預期，刺激聯想股價大漲。同系聯想控股(03396)午後飆，收升12.05%，報16.46元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">舜宇光學(02382)午後升幅擴大，收升13.78%，報83.8元，升幅藍籌股中居第二位。分析員指公司迎來數項正向趨勢，包括其光學技術優勢可進入AI服務器CPO元件、Open AI光學訂單及Apple訂單。瑞聲科技(02018)升3.74%，報45.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">信達生物(01801)與輝瑞達成全球戰略合作，合約總額達150億美元，全日升11.36%，報83.35元，升幅藍籌股中居第三位，貢獻恒指22點。另一藍籌藥業股石藥(01093)升7.76%，報7.5元，升幅居第四位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_01801-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_01801-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信達生物2024年度年報</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">泡泡瑪特(09992)收升7.37%，報173.4元，升幅藍籌股中居第五位，董事長兼首席執行官王寧稱誓做世界級企業。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股回軟，中芯(00981)挫7.54%，報81.6元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 華虹(01347)插5.12%，報161.3元。A股半導體股下挫，影響港股。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">電動車股跌，理想汽車(02015)收挫4.3%，報57.85元，跌幅藍籌股中第二位，首季Non-GAAP盈轉虧，蝕21億元人民幣，多家投行調低目標價，摩通降目標價至56元，重申「減持」，稱市場競爭加劇 ; 小鵬汽車(09868)跌3.77%，報63.85元，首季Non GAAP虧損16.9億元人民幣，遜市場預期 ; 蔚來(09866)跌4.15%，報42.5元。龍頭股比亞迪(01211)升1.11%，報91.3元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-121226__source-web_理想汽車-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：理想汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/800x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-121226__source-web_理想汽車-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：理想汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
